(242, 'Adab Terhadap Guru', 'adab-terhadap-guru', 'Keagamaan,Pendidikan', 'Adab Terhadap Guru', '<h2 data-sourcepos=\"1:1-1:21\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:normal;mso-outline-level:2\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/images/Red%20Minimalist%20Marketing%20YouTube%20Thumbnail%20(4).png\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 169px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">Menghormati guru merupakan kewajiban bagi setiap murid.&nbsp;Guru adalah figur penting dalam proses pembelajaran dan berperan dalam menuntun murid menuju ilmu pengetahuan.&nbsp;Berikut beberapa adab yang perlu diterapkan murid terhadap guru:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">Sikap dan Perilaku:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n	<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n     auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;\r\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">Menyapa dan Mengucapkan Salam:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\r\n     &quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\r\n     EN-ID\">&nbsp;Mendahului salam ketika bertemu guru,&nbsp;baik di dalam maupun di luar kelas.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n     auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;\r\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">Berpakaian Rapi dan Sopan:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">&nbsp;Menjaga penampilan dengan berpakaian rapi dan sopan saat berada di hadapan guru.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n     auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;\r\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">Duduk dengan Tertib:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">&nbsp;Duduk dengan tenang dan fokus saat guru sedang mengajar.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n     auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;\r\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">Menyimak dengan Baik:</span></b><span sty