(105, 'KH49d382bE', 'King Goheen', 'Dear smaipbsoedirman2bekasi.sch.id Owner!', 'anna@flawlessaura.online', 'Hi \r\n\r\nWe have freshly generated email leads from your niche and can set up a full email campaign for you using our sending systemâ€”all at a very low cost. We specialize in B2B and B2C email data generation and cold email campaigns\r\n\r\nWould you be interested in discussing this further?\r\n\r\nLooking forward to your response.\r\n\r\nBest regards,', '9:41: AM / 16-02-2025', 'Belum Dibaca'),
(106, '842b361d7K', 'Raina Trejo', 'To the smaipbsoedirman2bekasi.sch.id Webmaster!', 'nathalie@stafir-marketplace.com', 'Hello\r\n\r\nWe are interested in what you offer, can you send us your full offer? We are interested in long term cooperation.\r\n\r\nRegards', '7:39: PM / 04-03-2025', 'Sudah Dibaca'),
(107, '254dH9A7K3', 'Wulan Suci', 'Informasi Siswa Baru', 'wulandarmana@gmail.com', 'Selamat pagi,\r\n\r\nIzin ingin menanyakan apakah masih bisa melakukan pendaftaran untuk siswa baru? Dan apakah di SMA PB Soedirman khusus hanya menerima siswa muslim saja?', '8:53: AM / 02-06-2025', 'Sudah Dibaca');
