uot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">D.<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Akun instagram peserta lomba tidak boleh di private<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:67.65pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">E.<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Peserta wajib memfollow akun Instagram pangsud 2 bekasi dana kun bess<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:67.65pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">F.<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Peserta wajib memperkenalkan diri dan asal sekolah didalam videonya<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:67.65pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">G.<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Peserta wajib tampilkan video tag line &ldquo;sekolah nyaman ya soedirman!&rdquo; dengan seragam batik sekolah, masing-masing,<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>kirim video tag line ke email </span><a href=\"mailto:pangfest4.0@gmail.com\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">pangfest4.0@gmail.com</span></a><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"> <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:67.65pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Dengan mencantumkan subjek :<span style=\"mso-tab-count:1\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Tag line Pangsud 2 Bekasi<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:247.65pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n4.35pt;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Nama peserta :<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:67.65pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quo