so-bidi-font-style:normal\">freestyle</i> boleh menggunakan bagian tubuh manapun kecuali tangan<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n8.0pt;margin-left:67.65pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">I.<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">Dedline pengumpulan vid</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">e</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\">o tanggal 23 oktober 2020</span><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:67.65pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">J.<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1;background:white\">Aksi&nbsp;<em>freestyle</em>&nbsp;Anda dapat mencakup pergerakan menggunakan tubuh bagian bawa, tubuh bagian atas, dan sembari duduk. Alat-alat dan objek penunjang tak boleh digunakan dalam performa Anda (contohnya: tembok, tali).</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:67.65pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">K.<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;color:black;\r\nmso-themecolor:text1;background:white\">Anda harus mengawali aksi&nbsp;<em>freestyle</em>&nbsp;dari posisi bola mati.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:67.65pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">L.<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Bola yang digunakan harus bola sepak ukuran 4 (bola futsal) atau ukuran 5 (sepakbola)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:67.65pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">M.<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Perlombaan ini bisa kami batalkan seandainya tidak memenuhi quota tanpa pemberitahuan ke peserta terlebih dahulu, tapi akan kami umumkan di website<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:67.65pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">N.<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Semua berkas yang sudah dikirm jadi hak panitia<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:67.65pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-