t:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">J.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Wajib menggunakan tag line di awal video yaitu &ldquo;Sekolah nyaman ya soedirman!&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN\"> dan memakai baju batik asal sekolah. Jika tidak melakukan, akan didiskualifikasi.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:53.5pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">K.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Batas akhir pengumpulan tanggal 23 oktober<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n4.0pt;margin-left:53.5pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">L.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Jika melanggar peraturan yang dibuat akan dikenakan pengurangan poin sampai diskulifikasi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n4.0pt;margin-left:53.5pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">M.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Keputusan juri tidak bisa di ganggu gugat.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Video dikirimkan dengan cara : menyimpan video di drive, lalu kirim drive ke <a href=\"mailto:pangfest4.0@gmail.com\">pangfest4.0@gmail.com</a></span></p>\r\n', '05-10-2020', '04:08 PM'),
(50, 'Pendaftaran Online Pangfest 4.0', 'pendaftaran-online-pangfest-4.0', 'pangfest 4.0', '<p>Mohon dibaca persyaratan tiap perlombaan sebelum melakukan pendaftara. Pendaftaran dilakukan secara online menggunakan smartphone peserta lomba dengan link berikut ini :</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://bit.ly/formpangfest\">http://bit.ly/formpangfest</a><span class=\"bitlink--hash\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(238, 97, 35); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSebelum melakukan pendaftaran online, mohon dipersiapkan berkas :</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Foto Kartu Pelajar</li>\r\n	<li>Foto Surat Izin Sekolah</li>\r\n	<li>Nomor Telpon Guru Pendamping&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Foto Peserta (dapat selfie saat mengisi form pendaftaran)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Disarankan peserta mengisi menggunakan browser Chrome di smartphone masing-masing, agar dapat menggunakan fitur Camera saat input data kartu pelajar; surat izin sekolah dan foto peserta tanpa harus scan dokumen.<br />\r\nJika kesulitan dapat mengubungi panitia di bagian contact person di bawah ini :</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left:144.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-ID\">Rula Amelia&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"> :</span><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID\">081294407781 (wa) (sekretaris)</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Ro